                                    <condition>The fragment consists of 4 parchment leaves. The leaves are dark and torn. On <locus from="1" to="1" scheme="folios"/> ca 25% of the page has been cut from the outer margin resulting in loss of text. <locus from="2" to="2" scheme="folios"/> is intact, but has a cut through the parchment on the upper left side. <locus from="3" to="3" scheme="folios"/> is missing the bottom right corner, but no loss of text. <locus from="4" to="4" scheme="folios"/> is intact. All leaves are attached to the binding with paper strips.</condition>
